      "amount": "To taste",
      "notes": null
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onions and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, stirring frequently to prevent burning.",
    "Pour in the heavy cream and bring to a simmer. Cook for another couple of minutes until the sauce thickens slightly.",
    "Season with salt to taste and serve hot."
